## Image Optimization

### Recommended Formats

- **PNG**: Logos, icons with transparency
- **JPG**: Photos, complex images
- **SVG**: Icons, simple illustrations
- **WebP**: Modern format (smaller, high quality)

### Optimization Tools

```bash
# Install ImageOptim (Mac)
brew install imageoptim-cli

# Optimize images
imageoptim app/assets/images/**/*.{png,jpg}

# Install WebP tools
brew install webp

# Convert to WebP
cwebp app/assets/images/hero.jpg -q 80 -o app/assets/images/hero.webp
```

### Responsive Images

```erb
<!-- Serve different sizes -->
<%= image_tag "hero-background.jpg",
    alt: "Hero",
    srcset: "#{asset_path('hero-background-small.jpg')} 640w,
             #{asset_path('hero-background-medium.jpg')} 1024w,
             #{asset_path('hero-background-large.jpg')} 1920w",
    sizes: "(max-width: 640px) 640px,
            (max-width: 1024px) 1024px,
            1920px" %>
```

